Project Description
Animate.net is an application for creating 2D animations using vector graphics. It has a vector drawing interface similar to Inkscape and animation tools similar to Flash.

In Development

This project is currently in development. Developers are welcome to review the current source code and provide feedback. It has progressed a lot, but has a ways to go.
